full_description: Anaconda is built to advance AI with open source at scale, giving builders and organizations confidence to increase productivity and save time, spend, and risk. 95% of Fortune 500 companies and over 50 million users rely on The Anaconda Platform's centralized approach to sourcing, securing, building, and deploying AI. With 21B+ downloads, Anaconda is the gold standard for Python, data science, and AI—the enterprise-ready solution of choice for AI innovation.

